{"id":277313,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/奇闻录-帝都空气秒速美帝吸烟室/","date":"2013-02-01T04:45:33Z","modified":"2015-02-11T23:07:38Z","title":"奇闻录 | 帝都空气秒杀美帝吸烟室","content":"<p>彭博社今天刊发报道<a href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-01-30/beijing-air-akin-to-living-in-smoking-lounge-chart-of-the-day.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">《Beijing Air Akin to Living in Smoking Lounge: Chart of the Day》</a>（北京的空气就像在吸烟室），文章将北京1月份的 PM2.5 平均值与美国机场吸烟室的对比发现，北京的空气质量比吸烟室更糟糕。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/uploads/xiyan.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/uploads/xiyan.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" /></a></p>\n<p>数据显示，北京市一月份的 PM 2.5 日均浓度为每立方米 194 微克，并且在 1 月 12 日这天达到了最高 —— 每立方米 886 微克。相比而言，美国 16 个机场吸烟室的 PM 2.5 浓度为每立方米 166.6 微克。</p>\n<p>来源：彭博社</p>\n<div><a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?a=gcTc7pRyIE8:op9JhSezMfw:yIl2AUoC8zA\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?a=gcTc7pRyIE8:op9JhSezMfw:7Q72WNTAKBA\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?a=gcTc7pRyIE8:op9JhSezMfw:F7zBnMyn0Lo\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?i=gcTc7pRyIE8:op9JhSezMfw:F7zBnMyn0Lo\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?a=gcTc7pRyIE8:op9JhSezMfw:V_sGLiPBpWU\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?i=gcTc7pRyIE8:op9JhSezMfw:V_sGLiPBpWU\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?a=gcTc7pRyIE8:op9JhSezMfw:qj6IDK7rITs\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a></div>\n<p><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/qi-wen-lu/~4/gcTc7pRyIE8\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" />